It's just hard... hard to believe we've lost,

13:19.500 --> 13:21.500
一切都白费了
that it was all for nothing.

13:21.600 --> 13:24.100
可以不必这样
It doesn't have to be.

13:40.870 --> 13:42.300
看来
It looks like

13:42.370 --> 13:44.300
肿瘤长到海马体后面了
the tumor is nestled behind the hippocampus.

13:48.070 --> 13:50.000
你知道答案  迈克尔
You have the answers, Michael.

13:50.070 --> 13:52.170
问题是什么
What are the questions?

13:53.330 --> 13:56.100
我不知道  但你知道
I don't know, but you do.

13:56.170 --> 13:58.570
你只是还没有意识到
You just haven't realized it yet.

14:08.830 --> 14:09.930
前面右转
Up here, make a right.

14:10.000 --> 14:11.570
不  左转
No, no, left, left, left.

14:14.100 --> 14:15.770
我们还有10分钟  你觉得呢
We got ten minutes, what do you think?

14:15.830 --> 14:16.930
有点紧
It's gonna be tight.

14:20.830 --> 14:22.530
他们随时会来
All right, any minute now.

14:22.600 --> 14:24.230
没看到他
There's no sign of him.

14:24.300 --> 14:26.470
查一下怀肯的掌上电脑
Check Vikan's PDA.

14:26.530 --> 14:28.800
看看买家有没有留消息
See if the buyer left him a message.

14:28.870 --> 14:30.130
这个东西坏了
Oh, this thing is broken.

14:30.200 --> 14:32.500
肯定是他摔倒时砸坏了
It must have cracked when he hit the ground.

14:32.570 --> 14:34.270
还能看见号码吗
Can you still see the contact number?

14:34.330 --> 14:35.630
可以  是迈阿密的区号
Yeah, it's a Miami area code.

14:35.700 --> 14:37.530
读一下  我记到我手机里
Okay, read it out. I'll put it in mine.

14:37.600 --> 14:39.000
不  我不会读给你的
No, no, I'm not reading out anything.

14:39.070 --> 14:40.100
我暂时保留这个号码
I'm gonna keep that number

14:40.170 --> 14:41.530
你不介意的话
for now, if you don't mind.

14:42.630 --> 14:43.630
是谁
Who is it?

14:43.700 --> 14:45.100
我姐姐
It's my sister.

14:45.170 --> 14:46.870
不许接
Don't answer it.

14:46.930 --> 14:48.470
我说了不许接
I said don't answer it.

14:49.530 --> 14:50.800
开枪吧
Shoot me.

14:53.270 --> 14:54.570
喂
Hello?

14:54.630 --> 14:55.570
我们自由了
We're free.

14:55.630 --> 14:56.570
他走了
He's gone.

14:56.630 --> 14:57.570
什么
What?

14:57.630 --> 14:59.000
那个
The... the guy

14:59.070 --> 15:00.970
有只假手的人  他放了我们
with the, uh, fake hand... he let us go,

15:01.030 --> 15:04.000
所以我们穿过街  跑到普特的屋子里
so we, uh... we ran across the street to the Patels' house,

15:04.070 --> 15:05.630
几分钟之后  我往窗外看
and a couple minutes later, I looked out the window,

15:05.700 --> 15:06.630
看到
and I saw these, uh...

15:06.700 --> 15:08.430
两个人
these two guys in, uh...

15:08.500 --> 15:10.100
穿着西服  把他拖进货车了
in these suits, and they, uh, dragged him off

15:10.170 --> 15:12.200
行了  格雷琴  让巴格维尔接电话
into some van. All right, Gretchen, put Bagwell on the phone.

15:12.270 --> 15:13.930
-他不在那  -格雷琴  我可没开玩笑
He's not there. Gretchen, I'm not playing anymore...

15:14.000 --> 15:16.630
唐  "公司"的人抓住他了
Don, the Company took him.

15:21.000 --> 15:22.470
艾米丽怎么样了
How's Emily?

15:24.530 --> 15:25.800
她没事
She's... She's fine.

15:26.830 --> 15:28.500
听着  格雷琴
Listen, Gretchen.

15:28.570 --> 15:31.130
你得离我们远点
You need to stay away from us.

15:31.200 --> 15:32.470
为了所有的人
For everyone's sake.

15:32.530 --> 15:33.970
给  宝贝
Here, baby.

15:34.030 --> 15:36.100
再见  阿姨
Bye, Auntie.

15:40.200 --> 15:42.200
别管巴格维尔那个乡巴佬
Forget that hick, Bagwell.

15:42.270 --> 15:44.270
不  不行
No, I can't.

15:44.330 --> 15:46.900
他知道交易地点
He knows the location of the exchange.

15:46.970 --> 15:49.170
如果他知道我们在这
If he knows we're here...

15:49.230 --> 15:51.130
那么"公司"也知道
then the Company does, too.

16:00.900 --> 16:01.830
那就是
Hey, that's it.

16:01.900 --> 16:03.570
就在那  阿林顿码头
Right there-- Arlington Pier.

16:03.670 --> 16:04.630
靠边停
Pull over.

16:39.300 --> 16:40.370
血  兄弟
Blood, papi.

16:40.430 --> 16:41.930
我们刚刚错过了
We just missed them.

16:43.470 --> 16:44.900
我去附近看看
I'll go look around.

16:50.800 --> 16:52.100
指挥部
Operations.

16:52.170 --> 16:53.900
将军说  如果有需要就打这个电话
The General said to call this number if I needed help.

16:53.970 --> 16:55.730
请说您的通行码
Your clearance code, please.

16:55.800 --> 16:57.430
通行码
Clearance code?

16:57.500 --> 16:59.730
我是林肯·布伦斯  你将失去"锡拉"如何
How about I'm Lincoln Burrows and you're about to lose Scylla?

17:00.770 --> 17:02.500
通过
Proceed.

17:02.570 --> 17:04.030
我要追踪这条线
I need to trace this line.

17:04.100 --> 17:05.170
我们试过了
We've already tried.

17:05.230 --> 17:06.400
你所在的区域
You're in a zone

17:06.470 --> 17:07.730
无法进行视频监控
where visual surveillance is an impossibility.

17:07.800 --> 17:09.000
那就在区域外
Well, how about you look

17:09.070 --> 17:10.970
查找过去15分钟内
outside the zone and check for a vehicle leaving

17:11.030 --> 17:12.270
离开的车辆
in the last 15 minutes.

17:12.330 --> 17:14.430
如果有  核对一下  再给我电话
If you see one, get a match and call me.

17:16.630 --> 17:17.700
没发现
Nothing.

17:17.770 --> 17:19.170
没有痕迹  不过我找到这些
No tracks, but I found these.

17:19.230 --> 17:21.230
他们知道我们在找他们
They know we're onto them.

17:21.300 --> 17:24.100
我们要在他们分开前找到他们
We got to find these people before they split.

17:37.770 --> 17:39.900
有人在  但不是卖方
Someone's here, but it's not the seller.

17:39.970 --> 17:42.270
我该怎么做
What do you want me to do?

17:52.100 --> 17:53.830
我只是很好奇  朗格
I'm just curious, Lang.

17:53.900 --> 17:56.230
你什么时候决定背叛我的
When did you decide to turn your back on me?

17:56.300 --> 17:58.030
估计在你决定
Probably about the same time

17:58.100 --> 17:59.330
变成逃犯的同时吧
you decided to become a fugitive.

17:59.400 --> 18:01.200
我没跟你说话
I wasn't talking to you.

18:01.270 --> 18:03.170
我立过誓要维护法律  阿历克斯
I took an oath to uphold the law, Alex.

18:03.230 --> 18:04.700
为了升职吗
Did you do it for a promotion?

18:04.770 --> 18:07.130
为了抓我  他们答应你什么了
Did they promise you anything to serve me up?

18:07.200 --> 18:10.230
我只想让你安全  阿历克斯
The only thing I ever wanted was your safety, Alex.

18:12.030 --> 18:13.330
你逃跑时间越长
The longer you're on the run,

18:13.400 --> 18:15.700
我实现目标的机会就越少
the lower my chance of getting what I want.

18:22.870 --> 18:24.730
你往外看什么  阿历克斯
What you looking for out there, Alex?

18:26.570 --> 18:28.070
那里
There.

18:37.830 --> 18:39.770
我是惠勒特工  有个嫌疑犯
Agent Wheeler. I've got a suspect

18:39.830 --> 18:41.600
在拘禁期间逃跑
fleeing custody off Route 14

18:41.670 --> 18:43.000
格林伯格以南3公里14号公路
about three miles north of Greenburg.

18:43.070 --> 18:44.400
请求空中支援
Requesting backup and air support.

18:58.100 --> 18:59.900
我不是有意吓你
I didn't mean to startle you.

18:59.970 --> 19:01.700
你在这干什么
What are you doing here?

19:01.770 --> 19:03.430
客户服务
Customer service.

19:03.500 --> 19:05.070
质量控制
Quality control.

19:05.130 --> 19:08.800
我希望能掌控一切
I like to keep a hand in all our theaters of engagement.

19:08.870 --> 19:10.770
说得就像个军人
Spoken like a military man.

19:10.830 --> 19:14.800
把人命看得跟演戏一样简单
So easy to discuss lives in the balance when it's just theater.

19:14.870 --> 19:16.930
我很欣赏你的忠诚  莎拉
I admire your devotion, Sara.

19:17.000 --> 19:20.470
我最看重这个
It's an attribute I value above all others,

19:20.530 --> 19:22.370
但我想知道
but I wonder...

19:22.430 --> 19:23.970
你忠诚的是信仰
is it the cause

19:24.030 --> 19:26.430
还是这个人
you believe in or the man?

19:26.500 --> 19:30.130
我是说  你是个空想家呢
I mean, are you an ideologue

19:30.200 --> 19:35.400
或者只是个难得有人垂青就死缠烂打
or just a silly schoolgirl following the brooding boy

19:35.470 --> 19:36.600
的傻女学生
who finally noticed her?

19:36.670 --> 19:38.130
我是个寻找
I'm the girl whose father was murdered,

19:38.200 --> 19:40.230
谋杀我父亲的混蛋的女生
who's looking for the bastard responsible.

19:40.300 --> 19:42.500
你希望我打几个电话
Would you like me to make a few phone calls,

19:42.570 --> 19:44.170
看能否帮你
see if I can point you

19:44.230 --> 19:45.900
指点迷津
in the right direction?

19:45.970 --> 19:48.600
你放心  他接受的
You can relax, he's receiving

19:48.670 --> 19:49.730
是最好的治疗
the best possible care.

19:49.800 --> 19:51.000
是吗
Is he?

19:51.070 --> 19:52.700
因为我从没看到这种仪器
Because I've never seen this equipment before,

19:52.770 --> 19:54.470
也从没见过这种方式
and I've never seen this procedure.

19:54.530 --> 19:55.830
这是实验性的  对吗
It's experimental, isn't it?

19:55.900 --> 19:58.270
可以这么说  但以前用过一次
Well, you could say that, but it has been used once before.

19:58.330 --> 19:59.900
那个病人活了多久
How long did the patient live?

19:59.970 --> 20:02.230
唐克雷蒂医生
Dr. Tancredi,

20:02.300 --> 20:06.100
我知道你怎么看我们的做法  但是记住
I know your opinion of the work we do here, but know this.

20:06.170 --> 20:09.170
要看事情的本质
Not everything is as it seems.

20:10.200 --> 20:11.800
而且  这个手术
And for what it's worth,

20:11.870 --> 20:15.500
让那个病人过得很好  很久
the patient lived a long, happy life.

20:32.130 --> 20:33.670
你在干什么
What are you doing?

20:33.730 --> 20:36.770
结构工程师的责任是
It is the job of a structural engineer

20:36.830 --> 20:38.930
让他所有创造的东西
to make sure everything he creates is designed

20:39.000 --> 20:41.930
能承受附加在上面的重量
to withstand the weight placed upon it.

20:42.000 --> 20:44.470
我在这建造的
What I've built here...

20:44.530 --> 20:46.570
不够牢固
does not hold up.

20:47.600 --> 20:48.800
如果你发现
If you discovered

20:48.870 --> 20:51.700
你建造的东西有缺陷
that a structure you built was deficient,

20:51.770 --> 20:54.830
你会拆了它
would you tear down the building

20:54.900 --> 20:56.800
还是设法修整它
or find a way to fix it?

20:56.870 --> 21:00.170
我试过修整
I've tried to fix it.

21:00.230 --> 21:03.770
我试过让事情按部就班
I've tried to make things right.

21:03.830 --> 21:07.970
但我做的只是加大重量
All I've done is add more weight to it.

21:08.030 --> 21:09.430
现在
And now...

21:11.500 --> 21:13.900
我也承受不住了
...now I can't take anymore.

21:16.630 --> 21:19.930
我想做的只是救我哥哥
All I wanted to do was save my brother's life.

21:20.000 --> 21:21.900
你做到了吗
Did you do that?

21:21.970 --> 21:24.030
是的
Yes...

21:24.100 --> 21:25.930
但是有多少人
but how many other people

21:26.000 --> 21:28.330
为了这件事而失去生命
lost their lives in the process?

21:28.400 --> 21:30.770
现在知道了
Knowing that now,

21:30.830 --> 21:32.530
你还会让他死吗
would you have let him die?

21:32.600 --> 21:35.000
不会
No.

21:35.070 --> 21:38.870
因此你觉得自己是个杀人凶手吗
And that makes you feel like some kind of murderer?

21:42.070 --> 21:43.530
可能吧
Perhaps.

21:44.930 --> 21:47.200
杀十个人  你是个连环杀手
Take ten lives, you're a serial killer.

21:47.270 --> 21:49.230
杀一千个人  你就是战争英雄
Take thousands, you're a war hero.

21:49.300 --> 21:50.700
这不是战争
This isn't war.

21:50.770 --> 21:52.400
你确定吗
Are you sure?

21:52.470 --> 21:55.070
只不过是"公司"的小黑名单而已
There's nothing more than the Company's little black book.

21:55.130 --> 21:58.870
名字  数字  行动报告
Names, numbers, operation reports.

21:58.930 --> 22:02.570
事情不能只看表面  迈克尔
Not everything is as it seems, Michael.

22:04.600 --> 22:06.200
但你知道
But you know that...

22:06.270 --> 22:07.730
不是吗
don't you?

22:20.800 --> 22:22.670
好了  我们得和买家
All right, look, we need to reestablish contact

22:22.730 --> 22:24.730
重新取得联系  告诉他发生了什么事
with the buyer, explain to him what happened,

22:24.800 --> 22:25.900
重新选个交易地点
and then set a new location for the exchange.

22:27.430 --> 22:28.600
我得说
I got to say...

22:28.670 --> 22:29.900
我很惊讶  唐
I'm amazed at you, Don.

22:29.970 --> 22:32.170
那么长时间  你从没想过了解
Yeah, all this time, and you never once asked to see

22:32.230 --> 22:34.300
-"锡拉"里的信息  -因为我不在乎信息
the information in Scylla. That's 'cause I don't care

22:34.370 --> 22:36.130
我只关心它的价值
about the information; I just care what it's worth.

22:36.200 --> 22:39.470
也许你担心  要是知道里面的信息后
Maybe you're just worried if you actually knew what was on it,

22:39.530 --> 22:42.370
你会想  买家是什么样的人
you'd have second thoughts about who you're selling it to.

22:56.030 --> 22:57.430
喂
Hello?

22:57.500 --> 22:59.700
布伦斯先生  我们有目标的情况
Mr. Burrows, we have a hit on the targets.

22:59.770 --> 23:01.600
路况监视器显示他们进了一家便利店
Traffic camera picked them up entering a convenience store

23:01.670 --> 23:02.870
在威利街14号
on Valley and 14th.

23:04.900 --> 23:06.300
看来他们留下蛛丝马迹了
Looks like they left a footprint.

23:43.670 --> 23:45.200
不许动
Don't move.

23:48.730 --> 23:50.800
干得不错  朗格特工
That's a hell of a job, Agent Lang.

23:50.870 --> 23:52.530
是你教我如何看穿
You're the one who taught me how to read the mind

23:52.600 --> 23:53.730
逃犯的思想  记得吗
of a convict on the run, remember?

23:53.800 --> 23:55.700
如果你把我带走  我就是死路一条
If you take me in, I'm as good as dead.

23:55.770 --> 23:56.700
你知道的
You know that.

23:56.770 --> 23:59.130
所以
So...

23:59.200 --> 24:01.170
我现在要逃走了
I'm gonna run now.

24:01.230 --> 24:02.930
如果你要阻拦我
And if you need to stop me,

24:03.000 --> 24:04.370
你就必须杀掉我
you're gonna have to shoot.

24:04.430 --> 24:06.170
别逼我
Don't make me do this.

24:06.230 --> 24:07.970
对不起
I'm sorry.

24:11.000 --> 24:12.930
他时他方再见  费丽舍
Another time, another place, eh, Felicia?

24:13.000 --> 24:15.700
我会扣下扳机
I will pull this trigger.

24:31.800 --> 24:34.030
发生什么了
What happened?

24:34.100 --> 24:36.030
他跑了
He got away.

24:36.100 --> 24:37.300
你看到他了吗
Did you have him?

24:37.360 --> 24:39.300
我
Uh, yeah, I...

24:39.360 --> 24:42.030
我以为看到他了
I thought I had him unless I...

24:42.100 --> 24:43.530
但是跟丢了
I just missed.

24:43.600 --> 24:44.830
你看到他往哪跑了吗
Did you see which way he went?

24:44.900 --> 24:46.200
还是连这个也跟丢了
Or did you just miss that, too?

24:47.300 --> 24:49.030
他朝东去了
He went east.

25:03.060 --> 25:04.460
-伙计  -怎么了
Hey, buddy. What's up?

25:04.530 --> 25:07.530
我在找一名高个黑色头发的女人
I'm looking for a, a tall chick with black hair

25:07.600 --> 25:09.700
一个男人  高个
and a guy-- tall guy, uh...

25:09.760 --> 25:11.400
看上去就像波仔小丑
He looks like Bozo the clown.

25:11.460 --> 25:12.660
你知道波仔和埃尔韦拉吗
You know, Bozo and Elvira?

25:12.730 --> 25:14.830
你们
You guys

25:14.900 --> 25:16.260
是警察还是什么
cops or somethin'?

25:16.330 --> 25:18.360
不是
Not even close.

25:20.660 --> 25:22.230
有印象吗
So how 'bout it?

25:23.900 --> 25:25.530
我不记得见过这些人
I don't remember anyone like that.

25:27.260 --> 25:29.130
现在呢  臭小子
How 'bout now, you punk?

25:29.200 --> 25:30.460
-现在呢  -好的  我说
-How 'bout now?! -Okay! Okay!

25:30.530 --> 25:31.800
他们买了个手机
They bought a phone, man.

25:31.860 --> 25:33.030
给我收据
I want the receipt.

25:33.100 --> 25:35.060
好的
All right.

25:41.730 --> 25:43.660
他们在路上
On their way.

25:43.730 --> 25:45.400
你知道买家是谁吗
You have any idea who the buyer is?

25:45.460 --> 25:46.960
不知道  也永远不会知道
No. And we never will.

25:47.030 --> 25:49.130
任何想盗取"锡拉"里的信息的人
Whoever's walking away with the information that's on Scylla

25:49.200 --> 25:50.460
都会不惜一切
will do whatever it takes

25:50.530 --> 25:52.460
避开公司的雷达
to stay below The Company radar.

25:52.530 --> 25:54.460
而且  你要是搞了别人的老婆
Besides, would you screw some guy's wife

25:54.530 --> 25:56.100
会把名片放在他的枕头上吗
and then leave your card on his pillow?

25:56.160 --> 25:59.100
你不就是这么对将军的嘛
Isn't that what you just did to the General?

25:59.160 --> 26:00.260
说嘛
Come on.

26:00.330 --> 26:01.500
我们经历了这么多
After all we've been through,

26:01.560 --> 26:02.960
就不能互相坦诚吗
we can't be honest with each other?

26:03.030 --> 26:04.430
你的小照片
Your little photo shoot.

26:04.500 --> 26:06.460
还有想偷第6张卡的馊主意
And your weak ass attempt at the sixth card.

26:06.530 --> 26:08.600
你就想让他知道你参与了  对吧
You wanted him to know you were involved, right?

26:08.660 --> 26:10.600
说吧  他惩罚过你
Come on. He punished you,

26:10.660 --> 26:13.060
对待垃圾一样对你  就像你父亲那样
