No, but Self and Gretchen do.

40:04.370 --> 40:05.570
好
Good.

40:05.630 --> 40:06.870
你有合作伙伴了
Then you've got your team.

40:06.930 --> 40:08.900
我不会为他们卖命的
I'm not working for them.

40:08.970 --> 40:10.830
我得对我的命令
You'll work with a basset hound in a birthday hat

40:10.900 --> 40:12.400
唯命是从
if that's what I tell you to do.

40:12.470 --> 40:14.400
这是一个雇员的职责所在
That's what being an employee means.

40:16.870 --> 40:19.230
你必须接受命令并全力以赴
You're determined and dedicated.

40:19.300 --> 40:21.100
但是你简历中的空白
But there are holes in your resume

40:21.170 --> 40:24.000
格雷琴或赛尔夫  甚至巴格维尔都能填补
that Gretchen or Self or even Bagwell can fill.

40:24.070 --> 40:25.570
你们都从我这儿拿了东西
Now, you all took something from me,

40:25.630 --> 40:27.400
你们必须物归原主
and you're all going to get it back.

40:28.830 --> 40:31.400
而且
Besides...

40:31.470 --> 40:34.430
你一个人是搞不定的
you can't handle this by yourself.

40:34.500 --> 40:37.800
我觉得你应该知道
And deep down, I think you know that.

40:38.870 --> 40:41.300
让他们在外面等我吧
Have them meet me outside.

40:43.400 --> 40:45.770
谁知道呢
Who knows?

40:45.830 --> 40:48.170
你可能会喜欢上这里
You may find that you like it here.

40:48.230 --> 40:49.770
怪事接踵而至
Stranger things have happened.

40:49.830 --> 40:52.270
在你家都发生过
They've certainly happened in your family.

40:52.330 --> 40:53.970
现在
Now,

40:54.030 --> 40:56.600
关于迈克尔
about Michael.

40:57.770 --> 40:59.930
你会告诉他吗
Are you going to tell him,

41:00.000 --> 41:02.000
还是我去
or should I?

41:11.770 --> 41:13.270
你拿到了吗
Do you have it?

41:13.330 --> 41:14.770
拿到了
In my hand.

41:14.830 --> 41:16.930
好  你知道该怎么做
Good. You know what to do.

41:33.570 --> 41:35.600
我上次去医院看你
Last time I saw you in a hospital,

41:35.670 --> 41:37.070
是在少年棒球队时  你弄伤了胳膊
you busted your arm in Little League.

41:37.130 --> 41:39.970
是的  滑二垒时
Yeah, some bruiser knocked me down

41:40.030 --> 41:41.170
几条大汉把我撩倒了
sliding into second.

41:41.230 --> 41:42.330
真遗憾
Sorry about that.

41:42.400 --> 41:43.530
但你恢复得很好  对吧
But you healed good, though, right?

41:43.600 --> 41:45.230
是的
Yeah.

41:45.300 --> 41:48.030
这次也一样
This will, too.

41:48.100 --> 41:50.030
无论你有什么计划
Look, whatever plan you're working on

41:50.100 --> 41:53.570
把我们从这弄出去  我们最好有所行动
to get us out of here, we better make a move on it.

41:53.630 --> 41:55.700
你出不去了  迈克尔
You're not getting out of here, Michael.

41:59.070 --> 42:00.230
什么意思
What do you mean?

42:00.300 --> 42:01.530
我做了个交易
I made a deal.

42:01.600 --> 42:03.430
用"锡拉"换回你的命
Your life in exchange for Scylla.

42:05.770 --> 42:07.700
你为什么这么做
Why would you do that?

42:07.770 --> 42:09.770
就像当初你刺满纹身
Same reason you covered your body in tattoos

42:09.830 --> 42:11.330
入狱救我一样
and-and broke into Fox River.

42:11.400 --> 42:13.200
这事不仅关乎你我
This is not just about us...

42:13.270 --> 42:15.600
就是我们的事  一直如此
That's exactly who it's about. It's all it's ever been about.

42:18.700 --> 42:20.730
我们为"公司"摆平这件事
We do this one thing for the Company,

42:20.800 --> 42:22.630
然后我们重获新生
then they set us up for life.

42:22.700 --> 42:24.130
你真的相信他们吗
And you actually trust them?

42:24.200 --> 42:26.130
我还能信谁
Who else am I gonna trust?

42:26.200 --> 42:28.130
政府  唐·赛尔夫那种人
The government? Guys like Don Self?

42:28.200 --> 42:30.500
我不想再看到挚爱亲朋离去  迈克尔
I'm done watching loved ones and friends die, Michael.

42:30.570 --> 42:34.070
"锡拉"并非我们所想的那样
Scylla isn't what we thought it was.

42:34.130 --> 42:36.770
-完全不同  -我不在乎
Not even close. I don't care.

42:36.830 --> 42:38.900
我不明白你怎么这么说
I don't understand how you can say that.

42:38.970 --> 42:41.200
因为唯一值得打拼的是家庭
'Cause the only thing worth fighting for is family.

42:41.270 --> 42:44.270
我会尽一切努力结束这一切
I'm gonna do everything and anything I can to end this,

42:44.330 --> 42:45.900
你  我  所有人
so you, me, all of us

42:45.970 --> 42:47.430
才能继续我们的生活
can get on with our lives.

42:47.500 --> 42:48.930
就凭你对"公司"的了解
You think you can do that

42:49.000 --> 42:50.630
你以为你能做到吗
knowing what you know about the Company?

42:50.700 --> 42:52.630
你想知道我对公司的了解吗
You want to know what I know about the Company?

42:52.700 --> 42:56.100
妈妈生前一直为他们卖命
Mom worked for them before she died.

42:58.000 --> 43:01.730
我只是继承家族事业
I'm just moving on in the family business.

43:01.800 --> 43:02.930
林肯  别这么做
Linc, don't do this.

43:03.000 --> 43:03.930
已经说定了
It's done.

43:04.000 --> 43:06.900
林肯  林肯
Linc? Linc!
